I"ã<h1 id="preview-preloader">Preview preloader</h1>

<p>After creating a preloader, you can preview how it will look like on the page.</p>

<p>Navigate to the application or switch to the <strong>Preloader</strong> tab.</p>

<p><span class="doc_image"><img src="/assets/images/preloader/preview.png" alt="createnew" /></span></p>

<p>Left-click on the <strong>Show preview</strong> button. Your page will open in a modal window.</p>

<p>To close the preview, press the <strong>Escape</strong> button on the keyboard or click on the cross in the upper right corner.</p>

<p><span class="doc_image" id="preview" onclick="showModal(this.getAttribute('id'))"><img src="/assets/images/preloader/preview_logo.gif" alt="preview_logo" /></span></p>
